314
00:14:18,820 --> 00:14:20,260
If you were together,

315
00:14:20,420 --> 00:14:22,340
my brother would be sad
for a few days at most.

316
00:14:22,580 --> 00:14:23,700
But what you've done

317
00:14:23,940 --> 00:14:25,260
will only make everyone unhappy.

318
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:27,940
