and are sacrificing for a buddy.

319
00:14:27,940 --> 00:14:29,420
You're childish.

320
00:14:29,980 --> 00:14:30,820
At this rate,

321
00:14:30,820 --> 00:14:32,420
my brother will hate you
sooner or later.

322
