if she hears it.

345
00:16:46,460 --> 00:16:47,380
How come the English tape I gave you

346
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:48,580
became pop songs?

347
00:16:50,420 --> 00:16:51,540
Mind your own business.

348
00:16:52,620 --> 00:16:53,300
Tell me.

349
00:16:53,540 --> 00:16:54,380
In the afternoon,

350
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:56,260
what did you and Chunsheng talk about?

351
00:16:58,380 --> 00:16:58,940
Proper business.

352
00:16:59,740 --> 00:17:00,740
What business?

353
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:03,420
He Hongling.

354
00:17:03,580 --> 00:17:04,420
Isn't that proper enough?

355
00:17:05,780 --> 00:17:06,570
Why did you talk about her?

356
00:17:07,540 --> 00:17:09,220
When I gave you this,

357
00:17:09,330 --> 00:17:10,780
what did you say?

358
00:17:11,180 --> 00:17:11,860
What did I say?

359
00:17:12,380 --> 00:17:15,420
You said we should be
with those we were fond of.

360
00:17:17,460 --> 00:17:18,660
I like He Hongling.

361
00:17:18,860 --> 00:17:19,980
I really like her.

362
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:22,940
But she doesn't like you.

363
00:17:24,500 --> 00:17:25,860
Just come to the point.

364
00:17:26,290 --> 00:17:27,420
Do you want to say

365
00:17:27,810 --> 00:17:29,700
you think that
He Hongling likes Xiao Chunsheng?

366
00:17:31,660 --> 00:17:32,860
I'm not the only one who thinks that.

367
00:17:32,860 --> 00:17:34,180
Everyone thinks that.

368
00:17:36,260 --> 00:17:38,180
And Xiao Chunsheng
likes He Hongling, too.

369
00:17:38,180 --> 00:17:39,260
You should be able to tell.

370
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:42,500
Guohua, you know it perfectly well.

371
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:43,420
Why do you do this?

372
00:17:43,700 --> 00:17:45,860
