just like you.

382
00:18:04,060 --> 00:18:05,540
What did I do?

383
00:18:06,580 --> 00:18:09,100
On the one hand, you think
you're better than Xiao Chunsheng.

384
00:18:09,420 --> 00:18:10,140
On the other hand,

385
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:12,140
you think you're not as good as him
almost in every way.

386
00:18:12,540 --> 00:18:13,220
Ye Fang,

387
00:18:14,300 --> 00:18:16,060
