431
00:22:24,780 --> 00:22:26,180
It's OK. I'm not tired.

432
00:22:27,620 --> 00:22:28,300
Mom.

433
00:22:28,780 --> 00:22:29,940
Mom, I'm home.

434
00:22:31,380 --> 00:22:32,700
Hongling, you're back.

435
00:22:34,060 --> 00:22:35,420
Let me do it. Go home.

436
00:22:36,420 --> 00:22:36,900
OK.

