Thank you for

457
00:23:28,220 --> 00:23:29,740
taking care of my mom these days.

458
00:23:33,340 --> 00:23:34,100
Here you are.

459
00:23:36,700 --> 00:23:37,420
What's this?

460
00:23:38,420 --> 00:23:39,740
I reckon the stuff you've brought to us

461
00:23:39,740 --> 00:23:40,580
these days

